	specs/formatter/report_spec.yaml.
	(EXTRA_DIST): Add specs/formatter/spec_helper.lua.
	* lib/specl/formatter/report.lua (footer): When there are zero
	passing expectations, don't trigger a DIVBYZERO, just report "No
	expectations met".
	* NEWS: Update.

